item.title: CNBC - Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang On How His Big Bet On A.I. Is Finally Paying Off - Full Interview
item.description: Jensen, thank you so much for being here today. And I want to get started just with a question that is really basic, but I think chips have been in the ecosystem a lot more lately, and there’s people who probably didn’t even really know what a semiconductor was a few years ago. Can you give me a very basic definition of what Nvidia is? Wow, that’s an easy question.
